{"tid":131660,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"巴西人妻探監 私處竟藏10米軟銅線33副耳機","createTime":"2017-02-23T08:19:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-23T09:32:38.000Z","uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b545769660c942998f4ed983bb65e3ed05f769df","tid":131660,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T08:19:23.000Z","msg":"<strong>巴西人妻探監 私處竟藏10米軟銅線33副耳機</strong><br />\n<br />\n巴西聖保羅一名囚犯妻子探監時，竟然在私處藏了近10米軟銅線、大量耳機和連接線，叫人嘖嘖稱奇。<br />\n<br />\n當局表示，位於馬丁諾波利斯（Martinopolis）的獄警向探監訪客進行例行檢查時，透過金屬探測器發現她私處有異物。這名囚犯妻子當場承認生殖器內藏有1包物件。<br />\n<br />\n獄警取出她體內包裹後，發現裡面竟然有33副耳機、17條耳機連接線和9.6米長的軟銅線，軟線全部捲成一團。她夾帶物品的動機不明，但已被帶往警局錄取口供，現獲准保釋。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20140306/640_a614ac4194d815b1cc0332ddd59d3dca.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20140306%2F640_a614ac4194d815b1cc0332ddd59d3dca.jpg&h=2513b20f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"201942e58a847fcd4b55b40e1023315d72ddd887","tid":131660,"uid":39365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T08:27:39.000Z","msg":"真係黑洞先裝到咁多野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3fc280d2b62a38bfd6b94a777464fe4c1f8e9e5","tid":131660,"uid":3023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T08:28:17.000Z","msg":"147 潮文?"},{"pid":"46795ac9895440278253bbdc8a157d96e6be7d99","tid":131660,"uid":50663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T08:30:50.000Z","msg":"算死草<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2fb27e4a7d0011aac0182c43740a3546f729eca","tid":131660,"uid":76776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T08:37:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ab57f299b09b33355c804e602ec451b2228595dc","tid":131660,"uid":28769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T08:44:09